task.en: In the project document, go to products and change my previous choice of the dishwasher to model B.
task.zh: 在这个项目文档中，找到products，然后把我之前打勾的洗碗机选项改成选择B型号的洗碗机。
task.ar: في مستند المشروع، اذهب إلى المنتجات وقم بتغيير اختياري السابق لغسالة الصحون إلى الطراز B.
task.ja: プロジェクト文書で、productsを見つけて、以前チェックした食器洗い機の選択肢をモデルBの食器洗い機に変更してください。
task.ru: В проектном документе найдите products и измените ранее выбранный мной вариант посудомоечной машины на модель B.

pre_command.en: osascript -e 'tell application "Pages" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Keynote" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to activate' && sleep 5 && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to make new document with properties {document template:template "Home Improvement"}'

grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to tell table 2 of sheet 3 of document 1 to get value of cell "C6"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "true" && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to tell table 2 of sheet 3 of document 1 to get value of cell "C7"' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "false" && echo "True" || echo "False"
